Syntax: phantomfist

Channels chi into a burst of speed, allowing your strikes to land before
opponents can react. Phantomfist is a chi-based buff skill available to
Pugilist-line characters (Monk, Brawler, Martial Artist).

Effects when activated:
  - Adds +2 to your chi pool.
  - Applies a +3 speed bonus for 2 combat rounds.
  - Activates a 10-round cooldown preventing reuse.

Speed improves how often your attacks land and your combat effectiveness.
The chi generated can feed into other chi-dependent skills.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Must have the Phantomfist skill learned.

See also: shelp phantomfist chakra flurry spinfist
